{"id": 2063, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心X爱彼迎】过年期间为了和父母更和谐地相处，你都是怎么做的？", "description": "想要和爸妈好好过个年，你得有些妙招。", "record_count": 8763, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171212173929xf2mjT4OUHtKQLk7.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-12-13T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 254473, "content": "多卖萌！", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1179295}, {"id": 253963, "content": "快点买机票在遥远的欧洲发祝福短信", "image": null, "praise_count": 95, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1185275}, {"id": 253964, "content": "我爸妈可潮了，还没放假呢，就要我春节带他们去日本转转，住住当地的Airbnb民宿，66666", "image": null, "praise_count": 845, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 733477}, {"id": 253965, "content": "只要说去旅游\n就没有什么Gap\n爸妈可欢脱了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 49, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 602753}, {"id": 253967, "content": "被赞数最多的前两名，软广痕迹不要太明显", "image": null, "praise_count": 134, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1211760}, {"id": 253968, "content": "我妈还差2年退休，要想带爸妈出国去玩也只能趁人山人海的春节和十一了。不过他们那么辛苦，现在兜里有点钱带他们出国玩玩享受一下也是应该哒！", "image": null, "praise_count": 169, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1053542}, {"id": 253969, "content": "多做事少说话，少看电视多拖地。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1050, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950816}, {"id": 253970, "content": "我爸妈越老心态越好", "image": null, "praise_count": 42, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1168185}, {"id": 253971, "content": "过年生娃给他们玩…哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 166, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1176704}, {"id": 253972, "content": "你们知道炸火吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1151252}, {"id": 253973, "content": "多带他们去吃好吃的！～～", "image": null, "praise_count": 137, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1156827}, {"id": 254230, "content": "我选择独自出走。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1212982}, {"id": 253975, "content": "给自己订好机票订好airbnb 让爸妈过年少操心我 就是我的爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 68, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 869045}, {"id": 253976, "content": "多吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 95, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1173153}, {"id": 253977, "content": "静静地睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 279, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1192764}, {"id": 253978, "content": "吃年夜饭时候不玩手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107204}, {"id": 253979, "content": "换个环境带他们玩玩", "image": null, "praise_count": 46, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1140460}, {"id": 253980, "content": "啥都听爸妈的，不做对，不搞事，跟着爸妈的领导走！有肉吃，吃的那么多，还堵不住嘴吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 236, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1108191}, {"id": 254748, "content": "多做事少说话，鸡鸭鱼肉吃过瘾，喝过瘾", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1098071}, {"id": 253981, "content": "陪他们去走亲访友，给足面子??", "image": null, "praise_count": 64, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107203}, {"id": 253982, "content": "出国旅游躲串门，然鹅爸妈吃不惯外国菜，so┑(￣Д ￣)┍ 上次去伦敦顶着被骂的风险偷偷订了民宿给他们，有厨房可以自己煮便餐，结果他们出乎意料的满意，光速打脸哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 103, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1211791}, {"id": 253983, "content": "考试不挂科，", "image": null, "praise_count": 177, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1211576}, {"id": 253986, "content": "很想出去玩，但是过年家里客人太多", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1122421}, {"id": 253987, "content": "少玩游戏，少看手机，帮忙下厨做家务，多陪爸妈说说话", "image": null, "praise_count": 137, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1190893}, {"id": 253988, "content": "…………水军的文案功力好差", "image": null, "praise_count": 85, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1023664}, {"id": 253989, "content": "告诉他们“有对象了，在老家过年”", "image": null, "praise_count": 47, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1191339}, {"id": 253990, "content": "包红包，让他们想去哪玩就能去哪玩", "image": null, "praise_count": 47, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 125548}, {"id": 253991, "content": "小时候总是爸妈提议带着我过年出去旅游，现在终于可以我带他们出国玩儿了！把这些年自己看到的世界都介绍给他们，有种梦想成真的感觉。", "image": null, "praise_count": 59, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1211810}, {"id": 253992, "content": "少在父母面前出现，出现了就积极干家务", "image": null, "praise_count": 58, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107227}, {"id": 253993, "content": "多帮她们做做事。", "image": null, "praise_count": 47, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107320}, {"id": 253994, "content": "包个大红包，让他们出去有谈资～陪着走亲访友", "image": null, "praise_count": 50, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1208858}, {"id": 253995, "content": "认真学习，努力干活，积极向上，任劳任怨", "image": null, "praise_count": 46, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1156643}, {"id": 253996, "content": "她们说啥就是啥", "image": null, "praise_count": 50, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1155928}, {"id": 254764, "content": "乖乖穿上棉毛裤", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1215655}, {"id": 253997, "content": "在家尽量分担家务～然后规划假期吃喝玩乐行程！", "image": null, "praise_count": 46, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1024356}, {"id": 253998, "content": "眼不见为静", "image": null, "praise_count": 49, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1111809}, {"id": 253999, "content": "专心陪他们看春晚和春节七天乐?", "image": null, "praise_count": 55, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1191044}, {"id": 254001, "content": "有质量地一起度过一两天就好", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1210106}, {"id": 254257, "content": "广告真实硬邦邦\r\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 609757}, {"id": 254769, "content": "不回家，，，，", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1215754}, {"id": 254002, "content": "换个环境，离七八姑婆亲戚远一点", "image": null, "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 814778}, {"id": 254004, "content": "啥都听话", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1108190}, {"id": 254006, "content": "好奇心一直吵着带父母去日本给airbnb做广告烦死", "image": null, "praise_count": 115, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 591764}, {"id": 254774, "content": "学习，大三狗，为了跟父母和平相处，每天学习干活不顶嘴", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1215809}, {"id": 254007, "content": "自觉的穿上绒裤", "image": null, "praise_count": 91, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 693297}, {"id": 254009, "content": "kk", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1189383}, {"id": 254010, "content": "家务我来做，司机我来当，红包我来给，保证父母美滋滋", "image": null, "praise_count": 51, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1211887}, {"id": 254266, "content": "能干兼职尽量干，做事放勤快点，少呆在家里", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1128319}, {"id": 254012, "content": "相处的时间越短越好", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1194612}, {"id": 254014, "content": "好奇心真的很努力，广告主爸爸他们没有功劳也有苦劳吧多打点钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 619239}]}